Because of this quarantine, information that traveled through the frequency bands of the higher dimen- sions would no longer transmit into the Earth's grid and cellular memory. Not only would the race memory from the Sphere of Amenti be unavailable to humans upon the planet, but interdimensional communications from higher dimensional fields would also be curtailed, as higher frequency transmissions could not pass through the Frequency Fence. As generations of the races evolved beneath the Frequency Fence, previous memory of humanity's involvement with and genetic relationship to extraterrestrial civilizations faded, and the advantages of technological advancement those relationships allowed were lost.
